      "id": 13664,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "@zhurig reported an SSRF issue in our logo generation on hatchful.shopify.com. This occurred because raw SVG data was being passed from the client via WebSockets, and then used when generating the logos. We have refactored this process to send only generic parameters about the customizations made by the user, rather than sending the SVG itself.",
